    <list id="eip-id1166815877613"><item>(a)  A student is selected at random. He is male and lives on campus. What is
the (conditional) probability that he is active in sports?</item>
    <item>(b)  A student selected is active in sports. What is the(conditional) probability
that she is a female who lives on campus?</item></list>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1171884546723">

